  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AutomationException
    AutomationException is a base class for all exceptions thrown by the Automation API.
    CommandException
    CommandException is thrown when a command fails.
    ConcurrentUpdateException
    ConcurrentUpdateException is thrown when a stack is updated concurrently.
    MissingExpectedEventException
    An exception thrown when an expected event is missing.
    NoSummaryEventException
    An exception thrown when a SummaryEvent is missing.
    ProjectSettingsConflictException
    Thrown when creating a Workspace detects a conflict between project settings found on disk (such as Pulumi.yaml) and a ProjectSettings object passed to the Create API.
    StackAlreadyExistsException
    An exception thrown when a stack already exists.
    StackNotFoundException
    An exception thrown when a stack is not found.
